the engines are two O-10 momopropelnat engines inside a cubic strut. two engines for more thrust and better thrustvector and the cubic strut to get an attachmentpoint. the engines use the monopropelant inside the 6 spheretanks (together with the rcs).i used my Fregat upper stage for this so it stil lhas a probecore and batteries inside the tanks above the engines.

the lander use normal LF/LOX Ant eninges.
